      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td width="100%" valign="bottom" height="35" colspan="4"><p style="text-align:justify;">
        <b>DELIVERY ACKNOWLEDGEMENT:</b> I, the customer/representative, hereby declare that I have the authority to enter into this agreement with the carrier/agents. 
